WEBVTT

01:30.990 --> 01:34.979
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.770 --> 01:38.450
[2004]

01:40.310 --> 01:40.840
Xiaolan.

01:40.840 --> 01:42.280
The original host is very sick

01:42.280 --> 01:43.310
and couldn't make it.

01:43.310 --> 01:44.070
You stepped up in this crisis.

01:44.070 --> 01:45.470
I am very grateful to you.

01:45.870 --> 01:47.070
If you are really nervous,

01:47.070 --> 01:47.509
just imagine the audience

01:47.509 --> 01:48.640
as big watermelons.

01:54.000 --> 01:54.729
Xia Xiaolan.

01:56.000 --> 01:56.870
Don't be nervous.

01:56.870 --> 01:57.729
I will help you.

01:58.310 --> 01:58.770
Come on.

01:59.240 --> 02:00.040
Are you ready?

02:09.070 --> 02:12.190
[Episode 19]
[Step Onto My Stage]

02:13.430 --> 02:15.280
May I ask, Ms. Wu Kaili,

02:15.280 --> 02:17.120
how much are you paid

02:17.120 --> 02:19.380
to be the brand ambassador for Elegance?

02:22.310 --> 02:23.280
So is it 10,000 yuan on their side

02:23.280 --> 02:25.030
and 100,000 yuan on ours?

02:28.280 --> 02:29.190
Were these reporters' questions

02:29.190 --> 02:30.650
not screened beforehand?

02:32.190 --> 02:32.750
Let's go.

02:33.030 --> 02:34.690
We've seen enough of the show.

02:34.870 --> 02:36.030
Don't be so impatient. Please.

02:36.030 --> 02:37.560
I'm so happy today

02:37.560 --> 02:38.470
that I almost forgot—

02:38.470 --> 02:39.280
I've prepared

02:39.280 --> 02:40.190
lots of generous little gifts

02:40.190 --> 02:41.560
backstage for everyone.

02:41.560 --> 02:42.360
I hope you can go

02:42.360 --> 02:42.870
and pick something you like.

02:42.870 --> 02:43.520
We don't want gifts.

02:43.520 --> 02:44.050
Alright?

02:44.400 --> 02:46.120
Thank you. Thank you.

02:47.190 --> 02:47.840
Thank you.

02:48.190 --> 02:49.520
Explain yourself!

02:52.030 --> 02:53.630
What's going on? Seriously.

02:54.560 --> 02:55.310
Exactly.

02:58.030 --> 02:59.360
Come on, let's have a drink.

02:59.360 --> 02:59.820
Cheers.

03:03.520 --> 03:04.190
Thank you, San.

03:04.190 --> 03:06.130
May you always have more than you need.

03:06.130 --> 03:06.990
Thank you, San.

03:11.400 --> 03:12.000
Are you...

03:12.280 --> 03:13.750
Are you that movie star,

03:13.750 --> 03:14.430
Teresa Li?

03:17.630 --> 03:18.160
Yes, I am.

03:18.400 --> 03:19.400
I'm your fan.

03:19.540 --> 03:20.800
-I'm... May I...
-San.

03:20.870 --> 03:21.520
Calm down.

03:21.870 --> 03:22.930
Keep a low profile.

03:23.870 --> 03:24.910
Alright, you guys enjoy your meal.

03:24.910 --> 03:25.680
Just wave me over if you need anything.

03:25.680 --> 03:26.010
Okay.

03:26.150 --> 03:26.880
Thanks a lot.

03:29.680 --> 03:30.140
Come on.

03:31.190 --> 03:31.710
Look at this.

03:31.710 --> 03:32.150
Xia.

03:32.960 --> 03:34.360
I'd like to propose a toast to you.

03:34.360 --> 03:36.090
Thanks to your brilliant plan,

03:36.190 --> 03:37.240
otherwise, we wouldn't

03:37.240 --> 03:38.770
have stolen the show today.

03:39.240 --> 03:41.000
Now I understand what you said that day:

03:41.000 --> 03:42.800
though Ji Ya was the one
who set the stage,

03:42.800 --> 03:43.630
the performer

03:43.710 --> 03:45.079
might not necessarily be her.

03:45.079 --> 03:46.680
Now that you mentioned performing,

03:46.680 --> 03:48.410
shouldn't you toast to Teresa?

03:48.470 --> 03:49.400
Her acting skills

03:49.400 --> 03:50.960
are truly masterful.

03:51.190 --> 03:52.430
When the reporters were chasing her
with questions,

03:52.430 --> 03:53.400
that aggrieved look

03:53.400 --> 03:54.860
was performed perfectly.

03:55.470 --> 03:57.520
It was all thanks to
your arrangement, Ms. Xia.

03:57.520 --> 03:58.030
Ms. Xia.

03:58.310 --> 03:59.630
I think you'd make

03:59.710 --> 04:00.750
a pretty good director someday.

04:00.750 --> 04:01.560
When that happens,

04:01.560 --> 04:02.750
I'll be your leading lady.

04:02.750 --> 04:03.150
Okay.

04:03.280 --> 04:04.800
Let's sign the contract now—

04:04.800 --> 04:06.120
in case you become too famous later.

04:06.120 --> 04:06.520
Zhou.

04:07.470 --> 04:08.310
Alright, Ms. Xia.

04:08.310 --> 04:10.310
I'll print the contract right away.

04:10.590 --> 04:11.050
Cheers.

04:19.600 --> 04:20.240
Eat up.

04:20.480 --> 04:21.610
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

04:29.240 --> 04:29.770
Mr. Chen,

04:30.360 --> 04:31.490
thank you for today.

04:31.560 --> 04:32.490
You're welcome.

04:32.630 --> 04:33.740
You coming to shoot the commercial

04:33.740 --> 04:35.200
really helped me out a lot.

04:35.310 --> 04:36.040
To be honest,

04:36.310 --> 04:37.600
I didn't expect

04:37.600 --> 04:38.800
you to agree so readily.

04:38.800 --> 04:40.000
After all, you are...

04:40.190 --> 04:42.250
An award-winning actress, you know.

04:42.560 --> 04:44.360
Then I'll be honest with you too.

04:44.950 --> 04:46.390
When I went on stage today

04:46.720 --> 04:48.120
and heard the audience cheering,

04:48.120 --> 04:49.630
I felt a little proud.

04:50.870 --> 04:52.720
But when Wu Kaili went on stage

04:52.920 --> 04:54.480
and I saw the audience's reaction,

04:54.480 --> 04:55.360
I realized the gap

04:55.360 --> 04:57.420
between myself and a real superstar.

04:58.120 --> 04:59.600
After our commercial airs,

04:59.600 --> 05:01.060
you'll be a superstar too.

05:01.720 --> 05:02.120
Right.

05:02.560 --> 05:04.090
I want to be a superstar too.

05:05.390 --> 05:05.800
Well,

05:06.240 --> 05:07.070
I'll be going now.

05:07.070 --> 05:08.110
See you next time, Mr. Chen.

05:08.110 --> 05:08.750
See you.

05:13.920 --> 05:14.360
Sir,

05:14.390 --> 05:15.190
please be careful on the road.

05:15.190 --> 05:15.990
Drive safely.

05:28.430 --> 05:29.510
Can't bear to see her go?

05:29.510 --> 05:31.390
Why not take her to the station then?

05:31.390 --> 05:32.680
It's true that I don't want her to leave.

05:32.680 --> 05:34.240
But she's a famous actress,

05:34.270 --> 05:35.830
and she'll be a superstar in the future.

05:35.830 --> 05:37.950
Even if I can see her off
at the station today—

05:37.950 --> 05:39.210
what about the future?

05:39.560 --> 05:40.159
Forget it.

05:40.560 --> 05:43.020
Let nature take its course.
I won't force it.

05:43.830 --> 05:45.159
Oh, so you're not forcing it, huh?

05:45.159 --> 05:46.120
I was thinking of

05:46.120 --> 05:47.480
creating a chance for you.

05:47.480 --> 05:48.340
Forget it then.

05:48.480 --> 05:48.750
Let's go.

05:48.750 --> 05:49.810
Alright, let's go.

05:49.950 --> 05:50.880
What do you mean?

05:52.390 --> 05:53.430
Are the school uniforms

05:53.430 --> 05:54.560
for donation ready?

05:55.120 --> 05:55.750
They're being loaded now

05:55.750 --> 05:56.750
in Longcheng.

05:56.920 --> 05:58.159
They'll arrive in 2 days.

05:58.159 --> 05:59.120
Alright. When the time comes,

05:59.120 --> 05:59.800
go to the donation site

05:59.800 --> 06:01.070
with Teresa.

06:01.360 --> 06:02.560
I'm sure some reporters

06:02.560 --> 06:04.430
will be willing to go with you guys.

06:04.430 --> 06:06.190
Her workplace seems to have learned

06:06.190 --> 06:07.650
about her donation today.

06:08.190 --> 06:09.600
People are gossiping,

06:09.950 --> 06:11.410
saying she acted on her own

06:11.480 --> 06:13.010
without getting approval.

06:14.510 --> 06:16.800
Even doing a good deed gets questioned?

06:17.890 --> 06:18.360
It's okay.

06:18.360 --> 06:19.600
Comfort her first.

06:19.800 --> 06:21.530
Once public opinion builds up,

06:21.630 --> 06:22.430
a good reputation

06:22.430 --> 06:23.760
will become her shield.

06:25.800 --> 06:27.330
What about the commercial?

06:28.190 --> 06:28.790
Just wait.

06:28.950 --> 06:29.550
We're off.

06:30.600 --> 06:31.060
See you.

06:36.040 --> 06:37.630
What's with that reporter Mr. Liu?

06:37.630 --> 06:39.600
Where's the big feature he promised?

06:39.600 --> 06:40.190
I contacted Mr. Liu

06:40.190 --> 06:41.680
as soon as I saw the newspaper.

06:41.680 --> 06:42.270
He said

06:42.290 --> 06:44.630
he wrote the article
based on newsworthiness.

06:44.630 --> 06:45.630
That Chen Xiliang

06:46.120 --> 06:47.870
claims Teresa Li donated money
on one hand,

06:47.870 --> 06:48.870
while saying it costs 100,000 yuan

06:48.870 --> 06:49.800
to invite a Gangdao star on the other.

06:49.800 --> 06:50.480
Isn't that clearly

06:50.480 --> 06:51.480
targeting me?

06:52.240 --> 06:53.120
Actors here

06:53.140 --> 06:55.000
get paid very little for filming.

06:55.630 --> 06:56.630
I don't believe

06:56.830 --> 06:58.360
she'd be willing to donate 10,000 yuan

06:58.360 --> 07:00.490
to buy uniforms for the students here.

07:02.000 --> 07:03.240
Can we get a reporter

07:03.360 --> 07:04.920
to interview that Teresa Li?

07:04.920 --> 07:05.600
As long as we can confirm

07:05.600 --> 07:07.260
her donation was fabricated.

07:07.510 --> 07:08.530
If Teresa Li's

07:08.630 --> 07:09.830
donation was fake,

07:10.190 --> 07:11.870
then that guy surnamed Chen from Luna

07:11.870 --> 07:13.270
is a fraud too.

07:13.870 --> 07:15.830
Businessmen all just want to make money.

07:15.830 --> 07:16.800
How could they bear

07:16.800 --> 07:18.120
to give any of it away?

07:21.000 --> 07:22.360
You might not know Xia Xiaolan

07:22.360 --> 07:23.270
well enough.

07:24.160 --> 07:24.890
I don't think

07:25.270 --> 07:26.000
she would leave us

07:26.000 --> 07:27.120
such leverage.

07:28.040 --> 07:29.360
If we really take a reporter

07:29.360 --> 07:30.560
to investigate Luna,

07:30.750 --> 07:31.680
but Teresa Li

07:31.800 --> 07:33.480
actually donated the uniforms,

07:33.480 --> 07:34.600
wouldn't we just be giving free publicity

07:34.600 --> 07:35.560
to Luna

07:36.000 --> 07:36.920
and Teresa Li?

07:38.070 --> 07:39.870
The most important thing right now

07:39.870 --> 07:41.530
is to get the newspaper to stop

07:41.560 --> 07:43.360
talking about Luna and Teresa Li

07:43.680 --> 07:46.190
and instead
give our Elegance's fashion show

07:46.190 --> 07:47.190
the upper hand.

07:48.310 --> 07:48.909
By the way,

07:49.510 --> 07:50.750
Teresa Li said

07:50.750 --> 07:52.510
she filmed a commercial for Luna.

07:52.510 --> 07:53.240
I wonder where

07:53.240 --> 07:54.190
it will be aired.

07:56.040 --> 07:57.970
Understood. I'll go investigate.

08:01.480 --> 08:02.080
Granny Yu.

08:03.950 --> 08:05.000
Do you think Xiaolan

08:05.000 --> 08:06.240
can really get the advertisement

08:06.240 --> 08:08.070
to be aired right after the news?

08:08.390 --> 08:10.040
If Xiaolan says she can,
then she definitely can.

08:10.040 --> 08:11.640
Let's have faith in Xiaolan.

08:39.510 --> 08:40.840
Why don't you turn it on?

08:42.480 --> 08:43.320
I don't care.

08:46.150 --> 08:47.120
I don't believe

08:47.600 --> 08:48.630
they can do it.

08:51.630 --> 08:52.230
It's time.

08:52.240 --> 08:52.790
It's on.

09:08.480 --> 09:09.960
Welcome to Luna.

09:11.600 --> 09:12.730
It's really airing!

09:17.950 --> 09:21.720
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

09:22.950 --> 09:25.270
♪ And sets my heart ablaze ♪

09:25.950 --> 09:28.240
♪ Are you also the same? ♪

09:31.450 --> 09:35.650
♪ Dreams will always shine ♪

09:32.270 --> 09:34.670
Luna looks forward to welcoming you again.

09:35.600 --> 09:37.440
Luna, Luna—a fashion legend.

09:36.550 --> 09:39.060
♪ There may also be regrets ♪

09:37.630 --> 09:38.750
Franchise Hotline...

09:38.750 --> 09:39.440
Looks pretty decent.

09:39.080 --> 09:42.830
♪ If you lose something,
be strong ♪

09:39.440 --> 09:41.000
0577-688888.

09:41.240 --> 09:42.370
Luna Brand Promise:

09:42.440 --> 09:43.670
for every item sold,

09:43.390 --> 09:45.790
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

09:43.790 --> 09:45.390
we donate 1 yuan.

09:46.080 --> 09:47.030
That number is easy to remember.

09:46.760 --> 09:49.300
♪ The dreams we dream in the day time ♪

09:47.320 --> 09:48.150
688...

09:48.480 --> 09:50.080
-888.
-888, symbolizing prosperity.

09:50.080 --> 09:52.680
♪ Is passionate yet naive ♪

09:50.320 --> 09:50.960
Xiaolan.

09:51.320 --> 09:53.360
That commercial you shot was awesome.

09:53.320 --> 09:57.810
♪ Our youth ♪

09:53.630 --> 09:54.600
That kind of creativity—

09:54.600 --> 09:55.440
I've never seen anything like it.

09:55.440 --> 09:56.770
Of course it's awesome.

09:56.840 --> 09:57.700
Let me tell you,

09:57.750 --> 09:58.840
when we were editing the shots,

09:58.300 --> 10:01.670
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

09:58.960 --> 10:00.750
even the director said
it was very imaginative.

10:00.750 --> 10:01.670
He said that nowadays,

10:01.670 --> 10:02.600
no one shoots commercials like this.

10:01.700 --> 10:05.140
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

10:02.870 --> 10:04.550
Actually, when we were filming,

10:04.550 --> 10:06.000
I didn't really like it.

10:05.350 --> 10:08.120
♪ We never give up ♪

10:06.360 --> 10:08.150
But watching it now,
it's really something.

10:08.150 --> 10:08.630
Ms. Xia,

10:08.740 --> 10:12.110
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

10:08.960 --> 10:10.440
you really should be a director.

10:10.440 --> 10:12.240
I've just watched a lot.

10:12.140 --> 10:15.290
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

10:13.150 --> 10:13.630
Well,

10:14.200 --> 10:15.600
have you all memorized the phone number?

10:15.320 --> 10:18.670
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

10:15.960 --> 10:16.560
Of course.

10:16.840 --> 10:18.370
0577-6 followed by five 8s.

10:18.840 --> 10:19.240
Zhenzhu?

10:18.860 --> 10:21.780
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

10:19.320 --> 10:21.030
0577-6 followed by five 8s.

10:21.720 --> 10:22.870
Even I've memorized it!

10:22.210 --> 10:25.370
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

10:22.960 --> 10:25.480
0577-688888.

10:25.590 --> 10:31.260
♪ That'd be enough ♪

10:25.670 --> 10:27.790
Right. 0577-6...

10:28.030 --> 10:30.030
Followed by prosperity and wealth!

10:30.320 --> 10:31.150
This really worked out.

10:31.150 --> 10:31.670
Chen,

10:31.960 --> 10:32.870
just wait for the calls
to start coming in.

10:32.870 --> 10:33.400
Alright.

10:34.030 --> 10:35.150
This bowl is on me.

10:36.030 --> 10:36.630
My idol.

10:37.080 --> 10:38.030
When you came last time,

10:38.030 --> 10:39.360
I didn't get a chance
to take a photo with you.

10:39.360 --> 10:39.960
Today,

10:40.360 --> 10:41.820
can I take a photo with you?

10:42.220 --> 10:45.590
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

10:43.270 --> 10:43.910
Of course.

10:44.440 --> 10:44.840
Great.

10:45.510 --> 10:46.000
Qiang!

10:45.620 --> 10:49.060
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

10:46.360 --> 10:47.630
Camera! Get the camera!

10:47.630 --> 10:48.150
Alright. Coming.

10:48.150 --> 10:48.670
Qiang!

10:49.150 --> 10:50.030
Camera! Get the camera!

10:49.270 --> 10:52.040
♪ We never give up ♪

10:50.120 --> 10:50.650
Hurry up!

10:52.670 --> 10:56.030
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

10:52.790 --> 10:53.550
Hurry up!

10:56.060 --> 10:59.210
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

10:59.240 --> 11:02.600
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

11:02.730 --> 11:05.640
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

11:06.130 --> 11:09.290
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

11:09.510 --> 11:15.180
♪ That'd be enough ♪

11:19.840 --> 11:21.790
It's really convenient to have a car.

11:21.790 --> 11:22.670
This way, I can take you

11:22.670 --> 11:24.030
directly to the station,

11:24.030 --> 11:25.760
so you don't have to take a taxi.

11:26.960 --> 11:28.560
This is Ms. Xia's car, right?

11:28.750 --> 11:29.670
Yes, it is.

11:30.480 --> 11:31.940
When Luna opens 20 stores,

11:32.030 --> 11:33.030
I'll buy a car too.

11:33.510 --> 11:35.240
Going out to negotiate business

11:35.240 --> 11:36.480
will be more convenient,

11:36.480 --> 11:38.510
and people will think more highly of me.

11:38.510 --> 11:40.630
How many people do you think

11:41.030 --> 11:42.560
saw our ad that aired today?

11:44.080 --> 11:46.000
I usually don't switch channels

11:46.000 --> 11:47.240
right after the news.

11:47.550 --> 11:48.280
Don't worry.

11:48.720 --> 11:49.510
A lot of people

11:49.510 --> 11:50.630
must have seen it.

11:54.390 --> 11:55.600
After today,

11:56.000 --> 11:57.270
you'll be a superstar.

11:58.960 --> 12:00.240
I heard that those stars

12:00.240 --> 12:02.700
all have their own drivers
and private cars.

12:02.840 --> 12:05.550
I won't get to drive you around
in the future.

12:09.150 --> 12:09.840
Mr. Chen.

12:10.870 --> 12:12.150
About the future,

12:13.390 --> 12:15.520
don't jump to conclusions so quickly.

12:22.320 --> 12:23.000
Mr. Chen.

12:23.670 --> 12:24.870
Drive safely.

12:25.390 --> 12:25.750
Okay.

12:34.250 --> 12:35.330
The ad has aired.

12:35.360 --> 12:37.150
Give it a few days to build momentum,

12:37.150 --> 12:38.080
and franchisees

12:38.120 --> 12:38.840
will be lining up

12:38.840 --> 12:40.320
at Luna's door,

12:40.600 --> 12:41.630
and Chen Xiliang will be

12:41.630 --> 12:43.030
answering phone calls nonstop.

12:43.030 --> 12:43.690
Zhou Cheng,

12:43.810 --> 12:45.340
I'm just so happy!

12:49.120 --> 12:50.150
You haven't been drinking today.

12:50.150 --> 12:51.390
Why do you seem so tipsy?

12:51.390 --> 12:52.670
Because achieving a dream

12:52.670 --> 12:54.200
is intoxicating like that.

12:54.870 --> 12:56.320
Once Luna has

12:56.320 --> 12:57.380
over 50 franchisees,

12:57.380 --> 12:58.190
I'll pull out.

12:58.480 --> 13:00.150
Then I'll draw my own blueprints

13:00.150 --> 13:01.350
and do my own designs.

13:01.510 --> 13:02.890
I want to build the best houses

13:02.890 --> 13:04.090
in all of Shengcheng!

13:04.440 --> 13:06.240
I want to be a real estate developer!

13:06.240 --> 13:07.550
I want to be a designer!

13:10.150 --> 13:10.810
Zhou Cheng.

13:11.150 --> 13:12.480
Do you think this dream of mine

13:12.480 --> 13:13.600
is too big?

13:14.480 --> 13:16.080
Do you think I'm talking big?

13:17.670 --> 13:18.870
The Xia Xiaolan I know

13:20.080 --> 13:21.540
has always dared to dream.

13:21.960 --> 13:23.420
Back when she had nothing,

13:23.910 --> 13:26.710
she was already dreaming of
conquering the world.

13:26.910 --> 13:27.600
And now,

13:28.200 --> 13:29.200
she has carved out

13:29.360 --> 13:30.840
a world of her own.

13:32.960 --> 13:33.490
Xiaolan,

13:34.910 --> 13:36.640
dream to your heart's content.

13:37.960 --> 13:38.840
You deserve

13:38.840 --> 13:39.840
a broader future.

13:41.750 --> 13:43.210
No matter what you become,

13:43.840 --> 13:45.300
I'll be there by your side.

13:52.000 --> 13:52.960
One million?

13:54.480 --> 13:56.150
Where did you get that much money?

13:56.150 --> 13:58.080
Besides, we're a clothing brand.

13:58.330 --> 14:00.360
How did you convince Hua TV?

14:00.720 --> 14:01.630
Ms. Liu,

14:02.150 --> 14:03.600
just get ready

14:03.630 --> 14:04.890
for Luna's expansion.

14:05.440 --> 14:06.240
In this era,

14:06.600 --> 14:07.750
as long as you dare to dream,

14:07.750 --> 14:09.080
nothing is impossible.

14:10.150 --> 14:10.680
Alright.

14:13.280 --> 14:13.910
Why did Granny Yu

14:13.910 --> 14:15.240
go to bed so early today?

14:16.510 --> 14:17.720
She might be tired from the day.

14:17.720 --> 14:18.840
After watching the ad,

14:18.840 --> 14:19.780
she went back to her room.

14:19.780 --> 14:21.440
She's probably asleep by now.

14:21.750 --> 14:24.840
Then let's celebrate quietly.

14:26.000 --> 14:26.360
Here.

14:44.480 --> 14:46.680
Where did I go with Mom and Dad that year?

14:47.110 --> 14:49.170
Why is it that I still can't remember?

15:23.510 --> 15:24.550
Before I knew it,

15:25.490 --> 15:27.220
you've been with me for so long.

15:28.320 --> 15:30.180
Through every important moment,

15:30.510 --> 15:32.510
success or disappointment,

15:33.360 --> 15:34.620
you've been by my side.

15:36.240 --> 15:39.030
Maybe I can tell you everything.

15:41.790 --> 15:44.120
Wait, Xia Xiaolan, what are you thinking?

15:44.440 --> 15:45.240
In this era,

15:45.240 --> 15:45.870
how could anyone possibly believe in

15:45.870 --> 15:47.730
something like transmigration?

15:56.030 --> 15:58.200
But what if I give it a try?

15:59.390 --> 16:00.550
What if...

16:03.390 --> 16:04.790
Better not overthink it.

16:07.510 --> 16:09.550
One yuan will be donated
for every item sold.

16:09.550 --> 16:11.240
Can we really trust that donation?

16:10.250 --> 16:12.320
[Luna]

16:11.670 --> 16:13.840
I heard the uniforms Teresa Li donated

16:13.840 --> 16:15.320
have already been sent to the school.

16:15.320 --> 16:16.520
So how do they donate?

16:16.540 --> 16:17.600
They record every sale?

16:17.600 --> 16:18.550
How would I know?

16:19.550 --> 16:20.810
Someone's coming out.

16:23.670 --> 16:24.240
First of all,

16:24.240 --> 16:25.390
I'd like to thank you all

16:25.390 --> 16:26.600
for your support of Luna.

16:26.600 --> 16:27.480
I hope later

16:27.480 --> 16:28.630
you can line up properly,

16:28.630 --> 16:30.080
so you don't block traffic

16:30.080 --> 16:31.080
or affect

16:31.080 --> 16:32.240
other stores' business.

16:32.240 --> 16:33.630
Thank you for your cooperation.

16:33.630 --> 16:34.390
Let's go. Let's go.

16:34.390 --> 16:35.030
Quick, quick. Line up.

16:35.030 --> 16:36.430
Line... Line... Line up.

16:37.150 --> 16:38.200
Is it true that for every item sold,

16:38.200 --> 16:39.080
you'll donate 1 yuan?

16:39.080 --> 16:40.410
This isn't a scam, is it?

16:40.510 --> 16:42.200
Luna has always operated with integrity.

16:42.200 --> 16:43.240
We would absolutely never scam anyone.

16:43.240 --> 16:44.370
Please come inside.

16:44.440 --> 16:44.970
Let's go.

16:46.150 --> 16:47.000
Steamed buns! Steamed buns!

16:47.000 --> 16:47.960
Watch your step.

16:48.390 --> 16:49.000
Thank you.

16:49.000 --> 16:49.790
Thank you, everyone.

16:49.790 --> 16:51.250
Hot steamed buns for sale!

16:51.270 --> 16:51.730
Come on.

16:52.240 --> 16:53.600
Watch... Watch your step.

16:53.600 --> 16:56.120
[Office]

16:53.960 --> 16:54.560
Mr. Zhang.

16:55.960 --> 16:56.870
Right, right, right.

16:56.870 --> 16:57.320
Yes.

16:58.600 --> 16:59.870
Just follow the

16:59.870 --> 17:00.750
address on the business card

17:00.750 --> 17:01.670
and come on over.

17:01.670 --> 17:03.200
Thanks for supporting Luna.

17:03.200 --> 17:04.800
Alright. Goodbye. Goodbye.

17:09.440 --> 17:09.880
Hello?

17:10.640 --> 17:11.440
Mr. Li. Mr. Li.

17:11.480 --> 17:11.829
No.

17:12.160 --> 17:12.750
No, I mean...

17:12.750 --> 17:13.400
Jiang... Mr. Jiang.

17:13.400 --> 17:14.160
I know. I know.

17:14.160 --> 17:15.089
Hold on a second.

17:15.270 --> 17:16.200
Alright, alright.

17:16.200 --> 17:17.800
You can come over. Of course.

17:18.200 --> 17:19.550
Sorry about that, Mr. Jiang.

17:19.550 --> 17:20.750
There's a limit on the amount.

17:20.750 --> 17:21.950
Thank you. Thank you.

17:22.720 --> 17:23.109
Mr. Chen.

17:23.109 --> 17:24.310
Come take the calls for a while.

17:24.310 --> 17:25.160
Mr. Liu will be here in a second.

17:25.160 --> 17:25.790
I'll go meet him.

17:25.790 --> 17:26.450
Okay. Okay.

17:27.640 --> 17:28.310
Hello. Hi.

17:28.680 --> 17:29.270
This is

17:29.270 --> 17:30.600
Luna Clothing Co., Ltd.

17:30.830 --> 17:31.720
Chen Xiliang! Mr. Chen!

17:31.720 --> 17:32.960
We want to join Luna!

17:34.510 --> 17:35.550
I know, I know. I got it.

17:35.550 --> 17:36.640
Thank you, everyone. Thank you, everyone.

17:36.640 --> 17:37.640
Please be patient, everyone.

17:37.640 --> 17:38.880
I'm the General Manager of Luna,

17:38.880 --> 17:39.680
Chen Xiliang.

17:39.920 --> 17:41.380
We'll arrange for someone

17:41.570 --> 17:42.880
to speak with you one-on-one
in a minute,

17:42.880 --> 17:43.310
all right?

17:42.890 --> 17:44.620
[Luna Clothing Group]

17:43.680 --> 17:44.810
One moment, please.

17:45.640 --> 17:45.970
Okay.

17:46.110 --> 17:46.550
Mr. Chen.

17:46.550 --> 17:47.070
Mr. Liu.

17:47.200 --> 17:48.160
Come, please come in.

17:48.160 --> 17:48.550
Okay.

17:48.590 --> 17:49.680
Luna will make arrangements for all of you

17:49.680 --> 17:50.640
one by one.

17:50.750 --> 17:51.960
Just a moment. Right away.

17:51.960 --> 17:52.510
Mr. Chen,

17:53.070 --> 17:53.880
tell me about it.

17:53.880 --> 17:55.310
How did your idea

17:55.310 --> 17:56.920
of donating 1 yuan

17:57.510 --> 17:59.400
for every item sold come about?

18:00.590 --> 18:02.750
To be honest, I'm a bit embarrassed
to say this.

18:02.750 --> 18:04.110
When I first started making some money

18:04.110 --> 18:05.400
from clothing,

18:05.960 --> 18:07.240
my first thought

18:07.350 --> 18:08.610
was not about charity—

18:09.070 --> 18:09.670
I actually

18:09.790 --> 18:10.720
bought myself

18:10.720 --> 18:12.160
a cell phone right away.

18:12.210 --> 18:13.210
A cell phone, huh?

18:13.470 --> 18:14.670
Later, I was inspired

18:14.700 --> 18:16.170
by Ms. Teresa Li.

18:17.110 --> 18:18.160
I thought, if she could

18:18.160 --> 18:18.960
take her own acting fees

18:18.960 --> 18:20.110
and donate them

18:20.110 --> 18:21.310
without hesitation,

18:21.680 --> 18:22.510
then why can't I

18:22.510 --> 18:24.070
use the money I earned

18:24.400 --> 18:25.510
for charity too,

18:25.640 --> 18:26.840
to help those in need?

18:29.070 --> 18:31.720
So, Mr. Chen, regarding this promise,

18:31.720 --> 18:33.790
when do you plan to start fulfilling it?

18:33.790 --> 18:35.350
And when will it end?

18:36.030 --> 18:37.400
It starts today.

18:38.660 --> 18:39.750
And every month from now on,

18:39.750 --> 18:41.110
we will publicly announce

18:41.110 --> 18:41.830
our

18:42.920 --> 18:45.110
sales figures and donation amounts.

18:45.510 --> 18:47.000
I also hope that you, Mr. Liu,

18:47.000 --> 18:47.590
along with

18:47.590 --> 18:48.800
our other friends from the media

18:48.800 --> 18:49.620
and the TV station,

18:49.620 --> 18:51.150
can supervise us together.

18:52.490 --> 18:54.170
And as for

18:54.200 --> 18:55.860
when it will end, as you asked,

18:56.880 --> 18:58.080
let me put it this way—

18:59.350 --> 18:59.960
unless

19:00.160 --> 19:02.160
the brand Luna goes out of business.

19:02.750 --> 19:03.830
And even if

19:03.830 --> 19:05.290
Luna goes out of business,

19:05.350 --> 19:07.000
our donations won't stop.

19:07.510 --> 19:09.200
So, Mr. Chen,

19:09.550 --> 19:11.760
could you please disclose

19:11.790 --> 19:12.920
your brand's sales figures

19:12.920 --> 19:13.650
for October?

19:14.310 --> 19:16.640
Currently, in Shengcheng and Longcheng,

19:17.000 --> 19:18.400
we have 7 stores.

19:18.510 --> 19:20.440
The sales figures for last month are—

19:20.440 --> 19:22.280
we sold a total of

19:22.310 --> 19:24.790
5,765 items nationwide.

19:26.110 --> 19:28.510
5,765 items?

19:29.000 --> 19:30.830
So the monthly donation

19:30.830 --> 19:32.150
is over 5,000 yuan.

19:33.110 --> 19:34.510
And the amount of donation for a year

19:34.510 --> 19:36.240
would be 60,000 or 70,000 yuan.

19:36.720 --> 19:37.350
Mr. Chen,

19:38.070 --> 19:39.480
can you take responsibility

19:39.480 --> 19:40.680
for what you've said?

19:40.920 --> 19:41.960
Of course I can.

19:44.160 --> 19:44.920
Right now,

19:45.590 --> 19:46.550
I'm not capable enough yet.

19:46.550 --> 19:47.880
I'll keep working hard.

19:48.310 --> 19:49.440
If the brand Luna

19:49.440 --> 19:51.770
can continue to grow bigger and stronger,

19:52.000 --> 19:54.030
the donation amount will also increase.

19:54.030 --> 19:54.960
I look forward to

19:55.070 --> 19:56.680
the day when we can donate 10,000 yuan,

19:56.680 --> 19:57.340
50,000 yuan

19:57.440 --> 19:59.040
or even 100,000 yuan a month.

19:59.160 --> 20:00.790
Donate 100,000 yuan a month?

20:01.750 --> 20:03.030
So for a year,

20:03.030 --> 20:04.890
that would be over 1 million yuan.

20:05.830 --> 20:06.440
Mr. Chen,

20:06.830 --> 20:08.310
you really dare to dream.

20:09.310 --> 20:10.640
Can I take a photo with you

20:10.640 --> 20:11.440
as a souvenir?

20:11.480 --> 20:12.000
Sure.

20:12.350 --> 20:12.880
Alright.

20:20.080 --> 20:21.170
[Sold Today]

20:20.750 --> 20:23.080
That's 98 yuan for 2 items after discount.

20:24.480 --> 20:24.960
-Here.
-Alright.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.310
-Coming.
-Exact change.

20:26.310 --> 20:27.160
Thank you. Thank you.

20:27.160 --> 20:28.750
You want to try on this scarf, right?

20:28.750 --> 20:30.080
Let me help you put it on.

20:32.350 --> 20:32.830
Xia.

20:34.030 --> 20:35.690
Please come here for a second.

20:36.160 --> 20:36.760
Qian Ying.

20:37.200 --> 20:37.570
Come here.

20:37.570 --> 20:39.230
-Coming.
-Go on. Give it to me.

20:40.680 --> 20:41.480
What's wrong?

20:41.680 --> 20:43.200
I just called Longcheng.

20:43.310 --> 20:45.370
The numbers are about the same there.

20:45.440 --> 20:46.790
We've already promoted it on Hua TV.

20:46.790 --> 20:48.110
Why is the effect not
as good as I expected?

20:48.110 --> 20:49.440
I thought we'd sell out.

20:49.590 --> 20:51.160
I even stocked up so much inventory.

20:51.160 --> 20:52.550
Sales have already doubled today.

20:52.550 --> 20:53.590
What's the rush?

20:53.640 --> 20:54.570
Just be patient.

20:54.750 --> 20:56.280
This is just the beginning.

20:58.590 --> 20:59.400
Chen.

20:59.750 --> 21:00.550
If it were you,

21:00.880 --> 21:01.680
would you rush to buy clothes

21:01.680 --> 21:02.940
just from seeing an ad?

21:03.590 --> 21:04.590
You have to give consumers

21:04.590 --> 21:05.480
time to react

21:05.500 --> 21:07.030
and find our Luna store, right?

21:07.030 --> 21:08.550
We didn't put our address in the ad.

21:08.550 --> 21:10.280
They have to ask around, right?

21:10.590 --> 21:11.750
If we can maintain

21:11.750 --> 21:12.920
today's sales volume,

21:12.920 --> 21:14.000
in a year,

21:14.000 --> 21:15.800
we could sell 60,000 to 70,000 more items.

21:15.800 --> 21:16.510
And that's only with

21:16.510 --> 21:18.070
7 stores.

21:18.880 --> 21:19.680
Our focus

21:20.030 --> 21:21.430
is still on franchising.

21:21.790 --> 21:23.720
Only when the number of franchise stores
increase

21:23.720 --> 21:25.070
can Luna's brand effect

21:25.090 --> 21:26.550
truly expand nationwide.

21:27.790 --> 21:28.510
You have no idea.

21:28.510 --> 21:29.880
Today, there were over 20 people

21:29.880 --> 21:31.240
who came to ask about franchising.

21:31.240 --> 21:32.430
They swarmed around me—

21:32.430 --> 21:33.880
I even thought they were debt collectors.

21:33.880 --> 21:34.510
That sight

21:34.640 --> 21:35.920
even startled the reporter, Mr. Liu,

21:35.920 --> 21:37.240
from Jingcheng Evening News.

21:37.240 --> 21:38.750
Among them, aside from a few who were just

21:38.750 --> 21:39.550
talking nonsense
and watching the spectacle,

21:39.550 --> 21:40.240
I counted—

21:40.750 --> 21:43.440
there are at least 9 that are serious
about meeting the requirements.

21:43.440 --> 21:43.970
Alright.

21:44.270 --> 21:45.870
Just as we discussed before,

21:45.960 --> 21:47.090
before the ad aired,

21:47.200 --> 21:48.550
the franchise fee was 50,000 yuan.

21:48.550 --> 21:49.680
Now that it's aired,

21:49.790 --> 21:50.790
it's 80,000 yuan.

21:51.030 --> 21:51.440
Okay.

21:51.790 --> 21:53.590
I'll go back to the company right now.

21:53.590 --> 21:54.830
Why are you in such a hurry?

21:54.830 --> 21:56.380
The ones who should be impatient now
aren't us,

21:56.380 --> 21:58.200
but them.

22:00.720 --> 22:01.590
Alright, go back.

22:01.590 --> 22:02.830
Take your time. Be safe.

22:02.830 --> 22:03.240
Okay.

22:05.400 --> 22:06.070
What?

22:06.480 --> 22:08.140
Luna paid 1 million for the ad?

22:08.480 --> 22:08.920
Yes.

22:08.940 --> 22:10.510
I checked through several channels,

22:10.510 --> 22:11.440
and the feedback I got was the same—

22:11.440 --> 22:12.310
as long as the ad fee is fully paid,

22:12.310 --> 22:13.370
the ad can be aired.

22:13.480 --> 22:14.440
It's all standard contracts,

22:14.440 --> 22:15.840
no favoritism involved.

22:16.310 --> 22:17.510
How is that possible?

22:18.240 --> 22:18.790
I think she

22:18.790 --> 22:20.270
must have used connections.

22:20.270 --> 22:22.000
Where did she get so much money?

22:22.070 --> 22:24.070
It's 1 million we're talking about.

22:24.200 --> 22:25.200
Even George couldn't

22:25.200 --> 22:25.920
come up with

22:25.920 --> 22:27.250
a full 1 million at once.

22:27.790 --> 22:28.790
Baby, did you just

22:28.830 --> 22:30.000
say my name?

22:30.880 --> 22:32.210
What can I do to help you?

22:32.960 --> 22:33.440
Tell me.

22:33.880 --> 22:34.480
George.

22:35.000 --> 22:35.930
I need your help.

22:37.070 --> 22:38.600
I can't lose to Xia Xiaolan.

22:38.720 --> 22:40.560
We must advertise on TV.

22:40.580 --> 22:41.350
Do you know?

22:44.720 --> 22:45.120
Right.

22:45.790 --> 22:47.750
We need to open direct-sale stores.

22:47.750 --> 22:49.350
We need to open our branches.

22:49.550 --> 22:51.200
Wherever there's a store of Luna,

22:51.200 --> 22:53.240
there must be a store of Elegance too!

22:53.240 --> 22:54.110
Elegance.

22:54.200 --> 22:54.680
Okay?

22:55.070 --> 22:56.240
Elegance? Okay.

22:56.240 --> 22:56.750
Yeah?

22:56.790 --> 22:58.250
I'll do my best to help you.

23:02.240 --> 23:03.110
I'll handle it.

23:03.400 --> 23:03.750
Okay.

23:04.400 --> 23:05.530
Here's your change.

23:05.550 --> 23:05.920
Here.

23:06.310 --> 23:07.440
Here's your change.

23:07.550 --> 23:08.150
Thank you.

23:10.720 --> 23:11.250
This one.

23:13.070 --> 23:13.800
It's just...

23:13.960 --> 23:16.000
It's still that issue we just discussed.

23:16.000 --> 23:16.550
Hello, hello.

23:16.550 --> 23:17.310
Mr. Chen, hello.

23:17.310 --> 23:18.070
Here are our qualification documents.

23:18.070 --> 23:19.800
Okay, have a seat. Please, sit.

23:21.350 --> 23:22.030
Thank you.

23:22.270 --> 23:23.310
Please come again.

23:23.310 --> 23:24.880
Actually, location is very important.

23:24.880 --> 23:25.680
Hello, hello.

23:25.720 --> 23:27.120
Please sit. Come on, sit.

23:27.160 --> 23:28.690
You can just give this to me.

23:31.200 --> 23:32.110
Thank you.

23:39.480 --> 23:40.160
No problem.

23:41.920 --> 23:43.780
Wishing you prosperous business

23:44.550 --> 23:45.550
and great wealth.

23:46.590 --> 23:48.520
I'm sure we'll work well together.

23:50.790 --> 23:51.320
Zhenzhu.

23:51.590 --> 23:52.650
Here's your money.

23:52.790 --> 23:53.960
I'm returning it to you with interest.

23:53.960 --> 23:54.490
Count it.

23:54.590 --> 23:55.200
Thank you.

23:55.200 --> 23:55.860
Uncle Yong,

23:55.920 --> 23:56.880
thanks for your support.

23:56.880 --> 23:57.280
For me?

23:57.750 --> 23:58.680
That's too much.

24:00.310 --> 24:01.000
Wei, yours.

24:01.480 --> 24:02.480
Well, mine's too little.

24:02.480 --> 24:04.030
I just participated a tiny bit.

24:04.030 --> 24:04.970
No need to be modest.

24:04.970 --> 24:06.000
For this commercial to air,

24:06.000 --> 24:07.530
everyone played a big part.

24:07.790 --> 24:08.830
Attorney Zhou.

24:09.070 --> 24:10.240
I've added some money

24:10.240 --> 24:11.570
to your bankbook again.

24:12.000 --> 24:13.130
Thanks, Beautiful.

24:13.750 --> 24:14.680
Then can I trouble you

24:14.680 --> 24:16.010
to keep saving it for me?

24:16.680 --> 24:17.680
Sure, no problem.

24:18.160 --> 24:19.030
I'd like to propose a toast to everyone.

24:19.030 --> 24:19.750
Alright, come on.

24:19.750 --> 24:21.550
Ji Ya is asking around everywhere,

24:21.550 --> 24:22.440
trying to find out

24:22.440 --> 24:24.240
what kind of connections Luna used.

24:24.240 --> 24:25.720
I bet she never expected

24:25.960 --> 24:26.720
that we

24:26.720 --> 24:27.920
could raise 1 million.

24:27.920 --> 24:30.110
To be honest, I didn't believe it either.

24:30.110 --> 24:30.880
So today,

24:30.960 --> 24:32.110
I want to thank everyone.

24:32.110 --> 24:33.030
Xia, thank you too.

24:33.030 --> 24:34.270
Even though we're getting old,

24:34.270 --> 24:36.000
making money with young people

24:36.000 --> 24:36.830
is so much fun!

24:37.110 --> 24:38.070
Alright.

24:38.070 --> 24:39.530
Enough with the nonsense.

24:39.830 --> 24:41.200
We're each other's support,

24:41.200 --> 24:43.350
and we're partners
moving forward together.

24:43.350 --> 24:44.240
Here's to making big money together!

24:44.240 --> 24:46.440
-To making big money! Cheers!
-Cheers!

24:51.310 --> 24:51.840
The song!

24:52.270 --> 24:53.310
Quick, quick! It's that song!

24:53.310 --> 24:54.550
Let's go.

24:59.550 --> 25:00.410
I'm coming too.

25:01.160 --> 25:06.640
♪ I know my future is not a dream ♪

25:07.880 --> 25:10.680
♪ I live every minute to its fullest ♪

25:11.720 --> 25:14.470
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

25:15.140 --> 25:19.360
♪ My heart dances with hope ♪

25:19.910 --> 25:23.420
♪ Dances with hope ♪

25:25.060 --> 25:27.910
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

25:28.700 --> 25:31.860
♪ I live every minute to its fullest ♪

25:32.610 --> 25:35.210
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

25:35.700 --> 25:39.440
♪ My heart dances with hope ♪

25:42.030 --> 25:42.720
Granny Yu.

25:43.350 --> 25:44.720
Regarding the advertising fees this time,

25:44.720 --> 25:46.650
you offered the greatest support.

25:46.960 --> 25:48.790
Since Luna's first store,

25:49.160 --> 25:50.490
you've been helping me.

25:50.680 --> 25:51.680
Thank you so much.

25:54.030 --> 25:55.240
That's a lot of money.

26:02.030 --> 26:02.750
Granny Yu,

26:03.920 --> 26:05.830
do you have something to say?

26:07.310 --> 26:08.550
If you need my help,

26:09.030 --> 26:09.830
just say it.

26:47.960 --> 26:49.560
This is my daughter-in-law.

26:50.440 --> 26:51.750
This is my grandson.

26:53.510 --> 26:54.720
This is my son,

26:55.270 --> 26:56.310
Xu Zhongyi.

27:00.350 --> 27:01.440
Back then, he insisted

27:01.440 --> 27:03.040
on venturing out to Nanyang.

27:04.430 --> 27:05.760
It's been over 20 years,

27:06.640 --> 27:08.550
and there's been no news of him.

27:12.480 --> 27:14.010
Mother and son share a bond.

27:14.590 --> 27:16.270
I believe he's still alive.

27:18.400 --> 27:18.960
He must have

27:18.960 --> 27:20.310
run into some trouble,

27:20.440 --> 27:21.840
so he couldn't come back.

27:24.350 --> 27:25.030
Therefore,

27:27.070 --> 27:28.730
I've been guarding this home,

27:31.920 --> 27:33.350
waiting for his return.

27:36.960 --> 27:37.590
Granny Yu,

27:38.350 --> 27:39.750
whatever clues you have—

27:39.750 --> 27:40.880
tell me everything.

27:41.960 --> 27:43.360
I'll help you find Mr. Xu.

27:46.270 --> 27:46.920
Okay.

27:48.510 --> 27:49.200
Okay.

27:50.880 --> 27:51.510
Okay.

27:54.110 --> 27:55.440
Yes. If there's any news,

27:55.440 --> 27:57.240
please contact me immediately.

27:58.960 --> 27:59.310
Okay.

27:59.720 --> 28:00.320
Thank you.

28:00.960 --> 28:01.750
Okay. Bye.

28:04.880 --> 28:05.590
You really looked like

28:05.590 --> 28:07.050
an entrepreneur just now.

28:08.000 --> 28:08.960
I'm helping Granny Yu

28:08.960 --> 28:09.790
find someone.

28:10.160 --> 28:11.480
She said Xu Zhongyi took

28:11.480 --> 28:13.640
2 boxes of antiques to Nanyang
with him back then.

28:13.640 --> 28:14.800
I figured even if we can't find him,

28:14.800 --> 28:16.000
the antiques must be in circulation.

28:16.000 --> 28:17.510
So I asked a few auction houses

28:17.510 --> 28:18.640
to ask around for me.

28:19.270 --> 28:20.110
Antiques?

28:20.680 --> 28:21.590
There are many

28:21.590 --> 28:23.440
private antique shops in Jingcheng.

28:23.440 --> 28:24.510
Shengcheng should have them too.

28:24.510 --> 28:25.720
I'll ask around later.

28:25.720 --> 28:26.980
There should be clues.

28:27.310 --> 28:27.830
My man is

28:27.830 --> 28:29.560
truly both smart and handsome.

28:33.400 --> 28:33.800
Hello?

28:34.750 --> 28:35.550
Guess who.

28:37.750 --> 28:38.440
Du Zhaohui.

28:38.440 --> 28:39.840
How did you get my number?

28:40.070 --> 28:41.550
I heard you asked someone

28:41.550 --> 28:43.080
to inquire about antiques.

28:43.590 --> 28:44.480
For things like this,

28:44.480 --> 28:45.880
you should have asked me.

28:46.400 --> 28:47.920
You're truly well-informed.

28:47.920 --> 28:48.680
I get by.

28:48.960 --> 28:49.490
However,

28:49.510 --> 28:51.200
I have a big gift for you.

28:51.640 --> 28:52.570
Young Master Du,

28:52.790 --> 28:54.590
my boyfriend is right next to me.

28:55.640 --> 28:56.590
I know.

28:56.640 --> 28:58.100
It's not that kind of gift.

28:58.640 --> 29:00.030
You'll know when you get here.

29:00.030 --> 29:01.890
It's an absolutely big surprise.

29:02.590 --> 29:02.920
Okay.

29:04.550 --> 29:05.550
What does he want?

29:06.350 --> 29:07.790
He said he wants to give me a

29:07.790 --> 29:08.720
big surprise.

29:20.240 --> 29:20.750
Ms. Xia.

29:21.270 --> 29:21.800
Welcome.

29:21.830 --> 29:22.960
Please, have a seat.

29:25.790 --> 29:26.320
Sit here.

29:27.030 --> 29:27.750
Please.

29:30.750 --> 29:31.410
Du Zhaohui.

29:32.150 --> 29:34.240
I'm very grateful to you

29:34.480 --> 29:35.880
that Luna got to run ads in Hong Kong.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.280
You really did me a favor.

29:37.750 --> 29:38.750
In the future, if your company

29:38.750 --> 29:39.830
needs anything,

29:40.070 --> 29:41.400
as long as it's legal and compliant,

29:41.400 --> 29:42.860
I'll do my best to help you.

29:42.960 --> 29:43.550
Ms. Xia.

29:43.590 --> 29:44.850
No need to be so formal.

29:44.920 --> 29:46.440
Helping you with this small favor

29:46.440 --> 29:47.400
is my honor.

29:48.270 --> 29:49.240
And

29:49.480 --> 29:51.270
I believe in helping all the way.

29:51.270 --> 29:52.150
I have a big gift

29:52.240 --> 29:52.880
for you.

29:54.400 --> 29:55.110
Surprise!

29:59.550 --> 30:00.240
Come on out!

30:07.960 --> 30:09.360
Ms. Xia, you're here too?

30:10.430 --> 30:11.160
Mr. Du,

30:11.460 --> 30:12.830
you know Ms. Xia?

30:17.030 --> 30:18.430
What are they doing here?

30:19.000 --> 30:20.730
What to do with them is up to you.

30:21.450 --> 30:22.410
I, Du Zhaohui,

30:22.440 --> 30:23.720
hate those

30:23.750 --> 30:25.720
treacherous betrayers the most.

30:26.240 --> 30:27.270
Now that I know,

30:27.440 --> 30:28.700
how could I let them go?

30:29.880 --> 30:30.830
You two

30:31.440 --> 30:32.440
offending Ms. Xia

30:32.470 --> 30:34.330
equals offending me, Du Zhaohui.

30:35.820 --> 30:36.500
Mr. Du.

30:36.640 --> 30:37.590
I'm worthless!

30:39.350 --> 30:40.790
I only incited Kaili
to breach the contract

30:40.790 --> 30:43.030
to make some more money.

30:43.640 --> 30:44.200
Mr. Du.

30:44.590 --> 30:45.160
Ms. Xia.

30:45.270 --> 30:45.960
I was wrong!

30:46.000 --> 30:47.040
I was wrong.

30:47.070 --> 30:47.550
You two,

30:47.840 --> 30:48.790
please be the bigger person

30:48.790 --> 30:50.030
and spare me!

30:50.510 --> 30:51.720
In the past,

30:51.830 --> 30:53.720
I would have handled this myself.

30:54.200 --> 30:55.510
Now, I'm handing you two

30:55.510 --> 30:56.960
over to Ms. Xia.

30:59.590 --> 31:01.160
This is my gift to you.

31:05.200 --> 31:05.960
What are you doing?

31:05.960 --> 31:06.420
Stop it!

31:10.550 --> 31:11.000
Du Zhaohui.

31:11.000 --> 31:12.330
Are you out of your mind?

31:12.590 --> 31:14.320
What on earth are you thinking?

31:15.680 --> 31:17.440
Thinking of making you happy, of course.

31:17.440 --> 31:18.500
They betrayed you.

31:18.830 --> 31:20.890
Don't you want to teach them a lesson?

31:20.920 --> 31:21.650
To be honest,

31:21.720 --> 31:22.920
seeing them like this,

31:22.920 --> 31:24.270
doesn't it feel good?

31:26.000 --> 31:26.550
It does.

31:27.200 --> 31:28.550
It is pretty satisfying indeed.

31:28.550 --> 31:29.240
But I'm not the type to enjoy

31:29.240 --> 31:31.170
watching people fight each other.

31:31.960 --> 31:33.790
Yuefeng led Wu Kaili
to breach the contract.

31:33.790 --> 31:35.440
I'll find a way to strike back

31:35.680 --> 31:37.410
in business using legal means.

31:37.640 --> 31:38.640
I just want to

31:38.640 --> 31:39.750
run my business properly.

31:39.750 --> 31:41.750
Why are you trying to hand me a knife?

31:49.440 --> 31:50.170
Xia Xiaolan.

31:50.750 --> 31:52.410
You are really hard to please.

31:53.240 --> 31:54.510
You are tolerant of others

31:54.510 --> 31:55.550
but picky with me.

31:56.880 --> 31:58.030
Are you taking advantage of the fact
that I like you

31:58.030 --> 31:59.060
to bully me?

32:01.510 --> 32:03.000
Who's bullying whom here?

32:03.880 --> 32:04.640
Du Zhaohui.

32:05.480 --> 32:07.000
I appreciate your help,

32:07.640 --> 32:09.160
but our styles of handling things

32:09.160 --> 32:10.640
are completely different.

32:10.640 --> 32:11.300
Let them go.

32:14.830 --> 32:16.000
Ms. Xia and Mr. Du

32:16.440 --> 32:17.720
are not on the same side.

32:17.720 --> 32:18.980
We still have a chance.

32:20.030 --> 32:21.090
Ms. Xia, I'm sorry.

32:21.200 --> 32:22.590
I broke the rules.

32:22.960 --> 32:24.020
Please forgive me.

32:24.210 --> 32:25.170
I won't take

32:25.200 --> 32:26.380
Elegance's commercials anymore.

32:26.380 --> 32:27.400
If Ji Ya wants me to pay damages,

32:27.400 --> 32:28.400
I... I'll pay.

32:29.070 --> 32:29.510
Right.

32:30.920 --> 32:32.200
Take whatever commercials you want—

32:32.200 --> 32:33.600
it's none of my business.

32:33.920 --> 32:35.050
But I'm telling you,

32:35.440 --> 32:37.000
if you keep acting like this,

32:37.000 --> 32:38.240
your image will easily collapse,

32:38.240 --> 32:40.770
and your reputation will be ruined
in no time.

32:40.790 --> 32:41.350
Ms. Xia.

32:41.590 --> 32:42.920
Please be magnanimous.

32:43.000 --> 32:44.620
You're bound to achieve great success.

32:44.620 --> 32:45.350
Your brand

32:45.510 --> 32:46.590
will surely become popular nationwide,

32:46.590 --> 32:47.590
even worldwide!

32:48.070 --> 32:49.730
I don't want to see them again.

32:51.440 --> 32:51.900
Get out!

32:53.000 --> 32:54.030
All of you, get out!

32:54.030 --> 32:54.490
Come on.

32:54.920 --> 32:56.000
Fish him out.

32:59.550 --> 33:00.750
Hurry up and go.

33:00.750 --> 33:01.680
That way.

33:01.960 --> 33:02.350
Move.

33:04.920 --> 33:05.500
It's getting late.

33:05.500 --> 33:06.760
I should head back too.

33:06.880 --> 33:07.310
Wait.

33:09.000 --> 33:09.930
I want to ask you,

33:10.830 --> 33:11.480
is it that no matter

33:11.480 --> 33:12.350
what I do,

33:13.070 --> 33:14.670
you will never be satisfied?

33:16.230 --> 33:17.110
You helped me,

33:17.480 --> 33:18.480
and I thanked you.

33:19.070 --> 33:20.110
It's nothing against you.

33:20.110 --> 33:20.680
It's just...

33:20.680 --> 33:21.920
It's just that you won't like me.

33:21.920 --> 33:22.350
Yes.

33:23.750 --> 33:25.550
There's no point in lying to you.

33:25.830 --> 33:26.510
Du Zhaohui.

33:26.790 --> 33:28.310
I've already found someone I like.

33:28.310 --> 33:29.010
As for you,

33:29.680 --> 33:30.640
you can get whatever kind of woman

33:30.640 --> 33:31.440
you want.

33:31.790 --> 33:32.640
There's no need to

33:32.640 --> 33:33.570
waste time on me.

33:33.830 --> 33:34.560
I'm leaving.

33:36.000 --> 33:38.060
What do you like about that Jerk Zhou?

33:40.070 --> 33:40.960
His name is Zhou Cheng.

33:40.960 --> 33:41.510
I know.

33:41.830 --> 33:42.690
I hate his name.

33:43.270 --> 33:44.000
He's nothing but

33:44.000 --> 33:45.000
a small-time attorney.

33:45.000 --> 33:47.310
He's only slightly more handsome than me.

33:47.310 --> 33:47.970
Does he have money?

33:47.970 --> 33:48.590
Is he famous?

33:48.590 --> 33:49.510
Does he have connections?

33:49.510 --> 33:50.970
In what way can he help you?

33:51.200 --> 33:52.460
He can give me respect.

33:53.310 --> 33:54.570
Respect from a pauper?

33:56.960 --> 33:57.880
Do you know how Zhou Cheng and I

33:57.880 --> 33:58.880
met each other?

34:00.270 --> 34:01.110
Back then,

34:01.110 --> 34:02.480
I was just a poor,

34:02.750 --> 34:03.790
disgraced

34:03.790 --> 34:04.750
village girl,

34:05.280 --> 34:07.680
while he was from the Jingcheng compounds.

34:08.070 --> 34:08.920
He was smart

34:09.150 --> 34:10.000
and savvy.

34:10.510 --> 34:11.190
In one summer,

34:11.190 --> 34:12.989
he could earn tens of thousands.

34:13.320 --> 34:15.070
As long as he wants to make money,

34:15.070 --> 34:15.840
whether in Jingcheng

34:15.840 --> 34:16.699
or Shengcheng,

34:16.710 --> 34:18.110
he will have a place.

34:19.920 --> 34:22.070
They say
beauty is in the eye of the beholder.

34:22.070 --> 34:24.440
But for you, it's a cash cow you see,
isn't it?

34:24.440 --> 34:24.920
Whether I'm

34:24.920 --> 34:26.580
Xia Xiaolan from Dahe Village

34:26.650 --> 34:27.360
or Xia Xiaolan who graduated from Huaqing

34:27.360 --> 34:28.510
and works at Luna,

34:29.280 --> 34:30.110
Zhou Cheng's love for me

34:30.110 --> 34:31.030
never changes.

34:31.840 --> 34:33.639
He likes me for who I am right now.

34:34.230 --> 34:35.560
No matter what I become,

34:35.710 --> 34:36.800
he will support me.

34:38.840 --> 34:39.760
I like you, too.

34:40.760 --> 34:41.820
I support you, too.

34:42.230 --> 34:43.710
I'm richer and more generous than him.

34:43.710 --> 34:45.510
I can give you even better things.

34:45.510 --> 34:45.920
Right.

34:46.780 --> 34:47.400
You can give me

34:47.400 --> 34:48.840
more and better things.

34:49.510 --> 34:50.320
But you just

34:50.320 --> 34:51.760
want to use those things

34:52.190 --> 34:53.110
to mold me into

34:53.110 --> 34:54.770
the Xia Xiaolan that you like.

34:56.630 --> 34:57.630
Zhou Cheng has never

34:57.630 --> 34:59.230
asked me to change anything.

34:59.510 --> 35:00.910
This is his respect for me

35:01.190 --> 35:01.880
and for

35:01.880 --> 35:03.320
our relationship,

35:03.920 --> 35:04.710
and I want to love him

35:04.710 --> 35:06.070
with the same respect.

35:08.160 --> 35:09.000
Du Zhaohui.

35:09.920 --> 35:11.720
You probably don't understand.

35:11.760 --> 35:13.480
But precisely because you don't,

35:13.480 --> 35:14.480
there is even less of a chance

35:14.480 --> 35:15.360
for us.

35:16.710 --> 35:17.310
Pardon me.

35:17.360 --> 35:18.150
I have to go.

35:41.960 --> 35:43.230
It's so big,

35:43.230 --> 35:43.880
Xiaolan.

35:44.280 --> 35:45.760
I rented

35:45.760 --> 35:46.760
this whole floor.

35:46.920 --> 35:47.920
The rooms outside

35:48.000 --> 35:49.800
can be used as Yuanhui's office.

35:49.840 --> 35:51.800
Yuanhui is in charge of
Luna's interior design.

35:51.800 --> 35:54.150
And with so many prospective partners
coming by,

35:54.150 --> 35:54.960
it's high time we had

35:54.960 --> 35:56.000
a decent office.

35:57.360 --> 35:58.550
This is great.

35:58.670 --> 35:59.670
You're spurring me on

35:59.670 --> 36:00.880
to run Yuanhui well

36:00.880 --> 36:02.070
and take on more quality projects.

36:02.070 --> 36:03.110
Otherwise, I'd be letting down

36:03.110 --> 36:04.630
such a great office space.

36:05.330 --> 36:06.930
I'm also spurring myself on.

36:07.480 --> 36:09.400
Luna has 27 stores now.

36:09.710 --> 36:11.110
Once the store number reaches 50,

36:11.110 --> 36:13.240
I'll withdraw from daily operations.

36:13.400 --> 36:15.280
As Shengcheng develops faster and faster,

36:15.280 --> 36:16.630
if I don't speed up,

36:16.710 --> 36:17.840
I'll be left behind sooner or later.

36:17.840 --> 36:19.510
You want to open yet another company?

36:19.510 --> 36:20.440
Is Yuanhui still not enough?

36:20.440 --> 36:21.440
Our business

36:21.440 --> 36:22.480
will only expand further.

36:22.480 --> 36:23.760
So I think Yuanhui

36:24.000 --> 36:25.560
should still focus on

36:25.590 --> 36:27.110
decoration and renovation,

36:27.110 --> 36:28.360
striving to become

36:28.360 --> 36:29.800
a leader in the industry.

36:30.800 --> 36:31.670
What I want to register

36:31.670 --> 36:33.070
is a real estate company.

36:33.320 --> 36:35.360
You want to buy land and build houses?

36:35.360 --> 36:35.800
Yes.

36:36.510 --> 36:38.280
But it won't be easy.

36:38.550 --> 36:39.760
As for funding, qualifications and stuff,

36:39.760 --> 36:41.360
I have to take it step by step.

36:42.800 --> 36:43.590
Anyway,

36:43.710 --> 36:44.310
this place

36:45.000 --> 36:45.880
will be where

36:45.960 --> 36:47.360
my dream sets sail.

36:48.320 --> 36:50.380
This is where my dream sets sail, too.

36:53.630 --> 36:54.890
Why don't I see Ge Jian?

36:55.030 --> 36:56.360
I lent Ge Jian and the car

36:56.360 --> 36:57.360
to Zhenzhu and Wei.

36:57.360 --> 36:58.360
They are going to

36:58.360 --> 36:59.840
the lighting fixture factory
to discuss cooperation today.

36:59.840 --> 37:00.710
I thought having a car

37:00.710 --> 37:01.550
would give them more face.

37:01.550 --> 37:02.800
You're such a thoughtful boss,

37:02.800 --> 37:03.590
even lending your car.

37:03.590 --> 37:04.510
You're really something.

37:04.510 --> 37:06.630
I have shares in the materials center too,
after all.

37:06.630 --> 37:06.960
Yeah.

37:06.960 --> 37:07.480
Come on, Uncle.

37:07.480 --> 37:08.190
Let's go look around some more.

37:08.190 --> 37:08.590
Okay.

37:10.440 --> 37:12.030
This place is really great.

37:13.510 --> 37:14.280
What do you think,

37:14.280 --> 37:14.590
Uncle?

37:14.590 --> 37:15.960
It's really nice. Really nice.

37:15.960 --> 37:17.400
Every room is wonderful.

37:19.510 --> 37:20.190
Zhou Cheng?

37:20.760 --> 37:21.690
Uncle, Xiaolan.

37:22.150 --> 37:22.920
How do you like this place?

37:22.920 --> 37:23.900
You're really something, kid.

37:23.900 --> 37:25.880
You even managed to find this place.

37:25.880 --> 37:26.960
Riding that bike of yours

37:26.960 --> 37:28.560
to pick up our Xiaolan again?

37:28.920 --> 37:30.800
Can't you just buy a car?

37:31.150 --> 37:32.360
Didn't we make quite a lot of money

37:32.360 --> 37:34.000
reselling cigarettes back then?

37:34.000 --> 37:34.520
Uncle,

37:34.550 --> 37:35.680
I have all his money.

37:37.550 --> 37:37.960
Alright.

37:37.960 --> 37:38.760
You two go ahead and leave.

37:38.760 --> 37:39.550
I'll look around a bit longer.

37:39.550 --> 37:39.860
Okay.

37:39.860 --> 37:40.710
Okay, we're leaving then.

37:40.710 --> 37:41.280
We're off then.

37:41.280 --> 37:41.590
Okay.

37:41.590 --> 37:42.520
Bye-bye, Uncle.

37:49.030 --> 37:51.000
I was thinking about
when we first came to Shengcheng—

37:51.000 --> 37:53.150
that time when Sis Bai and Wei

37:53.150 --> 37:55.080
were almost scammed by smugglers.

37:55.230 --> 37:56.190
The four of us

37:56.760 --> 37:58.070
were also sitting right here,

37:58.070 --> 37:58.800
drinking beers

37:58.800 --> 38:00.130
and eating roast goose.

38:00.230 --> 38:01.490
It's only been 2 years,

38:01.800 --> 38:04.930
and you're already
reminiscing about the past, Ms. Xia?

38:05.280 --> 38:06.740
It's already been 2 years.

38:08.440 --> 38:10.070
Time really flies.

38:11.070 --> 38:13.920
It feels even longer than
the entire lifetime I had.

38:13.920 --> 38:14.510
So many things

38:14.510 --> 38:16.110
I never even dared to imagine

38:16.400 --> 38:17.320
have actually

38:17.710 --> 38:18.800
come true.

38:21.070 --> 38:23.130
You're saying strange things again.

38:23.150 --> 38:24.590
The Xia Xiaolan I know

38:25.400 --> 38:27.030
has already had great ambitions

38:27.030 --> 38:28.440
since her days in Dahe Village.

38:28.440 --> 38:28.920
What's there

38:28.920 --> 38:31.120
that even you wouldn't dare to dream of?

38:31.920 --> 38:33.720
Even those with great ambitions

38:33.880 --> 38:35.280
can be afraid sometimes—

38:36.150 --> 38:38.960
sometimes afraid of
not achieving their dreams,

38:39.480 --> 38:40.590
other times

38:40.960 --> 38:42.420
afraid of running too fast

38:42.880 --> 38:45.030
and having it all come to nothing.

38:47.540 --> 38:48.200
Zhou Cheng,

38:50.030 --> 38:51.560
have you never been afraid?

38:56.550 --> 38:57.000
I have.

38:58.360 --> 38:59.030
But

39:00.070 --> 39:02.330
I'm not afraid of ending up with nothing.

39:02.710 --> 39:04.110
What's gained is gained.

39:04.630 --> 39:05.230
Even if I can't

39:05.230 --> 39:06.430
hold onto it forever,

39:07.360 --> 39:08.620
I will always remember

39:08.760 --> 39:10.670
the feeling of seizing that moment.

39:10.670 --> 39:12.320
The next time I reach out,

39:13.190 --> 39:14.190
that feeling

39:15.480 --> 39:16.610
will make me braver.

39:21.550 --> 39:22.350
You're right.

39:22.880 --> 39:24.590
This moment is real.

39:27.960 --> 39:28.670
Zhou Cheng,

39:29.190 --> 39:30.850
you're also not quite the same

39:31.070 --> 39:32.330
as you were 2 years ago.

39:37.110 --> 39:37.800
How so?

39:38.110 --> 39:39.280
Have I become more handsome?

39:39.280 --> 39:39.940
Not really.

39:40.710 --> 39:41.230
No?

39:43.110 --> 39:43.970
Maybe a little.

39:48.320 --> 39:48.850
Xiaolan,

39:51.480 --> 39:52.280
actually,

39:54.030 --> 39:55.150
I've always had

39:55.800 --> 39:56.830
a fear.

39:59.670 --> 40:00.440
I like you.

40:02.660 --> 40:04.120
I really, really like you.

40:05.360 --> 40:07.090
From the moment I first saw you,

40:08.480 --> 40:09.740
I knew you were the one.

40:11.960 --> 40:13.090
Can I get to know you?

40:13.880 --> 40:15.080
My name is Zhou Cheng.

40:16.920 --> 40:20.630
♪ I don't know when it started ♪

40:17.030 --> 40:18.290
My name is Xia Xiaolan.

40:19.000 --> 40:19.920
If, I mean if,

40:20.660 --> 40:23.940
♪ But my world suddenly became bright ♪

40:20.840 --> 40:21.920
one day I can catch up with

40:21.920 --> 40:22.800
your pace,

40:23.920 --> 40:25.440
I hope you can seriously

40:24.070 --> 40:27.750
♪ In the second our eyes met ♪

40:26.510 --> 40:27.280
consider me.

40:28.480 --> 40:29.920
Could it really be

40:28.890 --> 40:30.940
♪ I knew it had to be you ♪

40:30.670 --> 40:33.280
that the game read my preferences

40:31.600 --> 40:35.170
♪ Fireworks paint the sky tonight ♪

40:33.890 --> 40:35.160
and custom-made

40:35.190 --> 40:36.670
a lover for me?

40:35.350 --> 40:38.260
♪ Yet you'd rather stand in the rain ♪

40:38.530 --> 40:42.260
♪ Every secret you keep inside ♪

40:39.000 --> 40:39.760
But

40:41.360 --> 40:42.110
I'm not sure

40:44.000 --> 40:45.230
if the timing is...

40:44.000 --> 40:45.260
♪ I gather slowly, one by one ♪

40:45.280 --> 40:45.760
Zhou Cheng.

40:45.280 --> 40:51.180
♪ Countless times,
I've tried to tell you ♪

40:47.920 --> 40:48.440
You are also the one

40:48.440 --> 40:50.570
I want to spend the rest of my life with.

40:52.140 --> 40:54.260
♪ Even if the world turned upside down ♪

40:54.280 --> 40:55.960
♪ I'd always find you ♪

40:56.350 --> 40:59.320
♪ My beloved ♪

41:01.250 --> 41:05.110
♪ I'd give anything just to see you ♪

41:05.130 --> 41:08.590
♪ I'd move heaven and earth for you ♪

41:08.620 --> 41:12.090
♪ I trust that time will lead me to you ♪

41:12.110 --> 41:14.110
♪ I can forget everything ♪

41:14.140 --> 41:16.000
♪ Except your eyes ♪

41:16.030 --> 41:19.670
♪ I see the moments we shared ♪

41:19.700 --> 41:23.070
♪ I hear you calling out our vows ♪

41:23.120 --> 41:27.010
♪ I believe, and I hope you do too ♪

41:27.030 --> 41:28.450
♪ Whenever I see you ♪

41:28.480 --> 41:31.860
♪ Our love echoes ♪

41:40.880 --> 41:41.760
Stop hiding.

41:42.190 --> 41:43.440
Who's there?

41:46.840 --> 41:47.510
Sis Bai

41:47.510 --> 41:48.590
asked me to come check on you

41:48.590 --> 41:49.510
and see if you were still drinking.

41:49.510 --> 41:50.880
Did I ask you to watch this?

41:50.880 --> 41:52.070
Didn't you look just now?

41:52.070 --> 41:53.400
Your eyes were practically popping out.

41:53.400 --> 41:53.880
I... You know what,

41:53.880 --> 41:54.840
my head's all wet.

41:54.840 --> 41:55.760
Did you drool just now?

41:55.760 --> 41:56.920
She definitely drooled,

41:56.920 --> 41:57.850
I'm telling you.

41:58.070 --> 41:59.600
Let me wipe your drool then!

41:59.630 --> 42:00.490
Sis, I'm sorry.

42:00.920 --> 42:02.480
Come here, let me wipe it!

42:02.480 --> 42:03.080
I'm sorry.

42:03.280 --> 42:03.740
Sis Bai!

42:03.960 --> 42:04.480
Sis Bai!

42:04.480 --> 42:05.680
I'm sorry. I'm sorry!

42:05.840 --> 42:06.900
Did you look or not?

42:16.000 --> 42:16.710
Zhou Cheng,

42:18.710 --> 42:19.510
after I hand Luna

42:19.510 --> 42:21.000
over to Chen Xiliang,

42:22.400 --> 42:24.200
let's get our marriage license.

42:25.110 --> 42:25.590
Okay?

42:28.320 --> 42:28.710
Okay.

42:38.880 --> 42:41.880
[Six months later]

42:41.320 --> 42:43.320
The magpies are chirping in the sky,

42:43.760 --> 42:46.150
and a new couple is about to
start their life together on the ground.

42:46.150 --> 42:46.960
Please give

42:47.070 --> 42:48.280
a warm round of applause

42:48.280 --> 42:49.000
and welcome today's

42:49.000 --> 42:50.320
happy couple

42:50.630 --> 42:53.190
as they make their grand entrance!
